videos.headline: Smart opens up scoring for Hawai'i
videos.description: Jared Smart is the recipient of the first touchdown of the game for Hawai'i in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smart opens up scoring for Hawai'i) 2019/12/24

videos.headline: Smart scores 2nd TD of the day
videos.description: Jared Smart scores his second touchdown of the first quarter with a 40-yard reception for the Rainbow Warriors.

videos.headline: BYU responds with TD of their own
videos.description: BYU pulls back within one possession of Hawai'i with a one-yard rush at the end of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU responds with TD of their own) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wilson powers in for BYU TD
videos.description: David Wilson powers in for the touchdown as BYU pulls back within a possession of Hawai'i in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wilson powers in for BYU TD) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawai'i WR lays out for catch
videos.description: JoJo Ward lays out for the diving Hawai'i catch late in the second quarter for the Rainbow Warriors.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawai’i WR lays out for catch) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU runs jet sweep for TD
videos.description: BYU runs the reverse jet sweep for a touchdown as they get to within three points of Hawai'i.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU runs jet sweep for TD) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU QB gets spun around midair
videos.description: BYU quarterback Zach Wilson attempts to dive into the end zone but is spun around by defenders and fumbles.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU QB gets spun around mid-air) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawai'i takes lead late on McDonald's 4th TD pass
videos.description: Cole McDonald finds Nick Mardner with 1:20 left to go in the game as the Rainbow Warriors take the late lead over BYU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hawai’i takes lead late on McDonald’s 4th TD pass) 2019/12/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hawai'i wins Hawai'i Bowl behind McDonald's 4 TD passes
videos.description: Hawai'i QB Cole McDonald tosses four touchdown passes and adds a rushing score as the Rainbow Warriors beat BYU 38-34 to win the SoFi Hawai'i Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Hawai’i wins Hawai’i Bowl behind McDonald’s 4 TD passes) 2019/12/24 ESHEET SOTFULL
